{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handlepushregistrationfailure:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handlePushRegistrationFailure:","role":"symbol","title":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}]},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handlePushRegistrationFailure:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSError"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The NSError received from APNs registration failure"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"error"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Call this method from your AppDelegate’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"application:didFailToRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithError:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to notify Pushwoosh about registration failures.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This allows Pushwoosh to:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Log the error for debugging"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Retry registration if appropriate","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Update device status in the Control Panel"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Example","text":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle registration failure with user feedback:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class AppDelegate: UIResponder, UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ application: UIApplication,","                    didFailToRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithError error: Error) {","","        \/\/ Forward to Pushwoosh","        Pushwoosh.configure.handlePushRegistrationFailure(error as NSError)","","        \/\/ Log for debugging","        Logger.error(\"Push registration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","","        \/\/ Handle specific error cases","        let nsError = error as NSError","        switch nsError.code {","        case 3010:","            \/\/ Simulator or push not supported","            Logger.warning(\"Push notifications not supported on this device\")","","        default:","            \/\/ Track error in analytics","            Analytics.track(\"push_registration_failed\", properties: [","                \"error_code\": nsError.code,","                \"error_message\": nsError.localizedDescription","            ])","","            \/\/ Optionally notify user","            if shouldShowPushError {","                showPushRegistrationError()","            }","        }","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Handles push notification registration failure."}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"type":"topic","role":"collection","title":"PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"PWConfiguration"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/handlePushRegistrationFailure:":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handlePushRegistrationFailure:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Handles push notification registration failure."}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handlepushregistrationfailure:","role":"symbol","title":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:"}],"type":"topic"}}}